➜航拍安徽肥东岘山秋色 环境治理重现乡村美景
http://www.sohu.com/a/430385080_162522	27985
<p><span>来源：<span>中国新闻网</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>
<p>2020-11-08 15:42</p>
<p><i><img src="//p8.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201108/450fe4cd83b34a3db5a02e8d48fb14f4.jpeg" /></i></p>
<p><i><img src="//p9.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201108/24e77e94ac1d4905af1861a05b712f76.jpeg" /></i></p>
